channel.title: I need some help guys...im in a pinch
channel.description:
ok...i was trying to create a new runescape account when i accidently selected my age as 12 and under...
now when i try and create a new account, it wont let me; it says "Sorry, you already told us you were under 13 and we stopped you from opening an account. We really meant it" those are the exact words..." can someone tell me how to fix this?
ive deleted my cookies, history, temp internet files, etc and nothings working...so some help please
i dont want to format my drive to get it to work...
P.S. i can still log in with my lvl 59 main
